### **Day 87**
- **Material:** `Cow<'a, T>`
- **Reading:** std::borrow::Cow docs (15 min)
- **Exercise:** (15 min)
```rust
use std::borrow::Cow;

fn process(input: Cow<str>) -> Cow<str> {
    if input.contains("special") {
        Cow::Owned(input.replace("special", "SPECIAL"))
    } else {
        input  // No allocation!
    }
}
```

